Class ModelManager

java.lang.Object
  model.ModelManager

public class ModelManager
extends Object

The manager of models available to IDES. This allows for custom model types implemented by plugins.

Author:
Lenko Grigorov

Field Detail

class2Model

protected static Hashtable<Class,Set<ModelDescriptor>> class2Model
Index of all registered ModelDescriptors. The key is the DES model interface implemented by the model. The value is the set of the model descriptors of all models implementing the given interface. Note that if a model implements a number of interfaces, its model descriptor will be included in the set for each one of these interfaces.
